      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can I exercise during the pre-op diet?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, light exercise like walking (20-30 minutes daily) is encouraged and helps manage hunger. Avoid intense exercise—you're on very low calories (800-1,000 daily) and will have low energy. Listen to your body. Exercise helps distract from hunger but conserve energy for healing."
      }
    },
