<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="hero-section">
  <h2 style="color: white; margin-top: 0;">Your Complete 2-Week Roadmap to Surgery Success</h2>
  <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); font-size: 1.125rem;">The pre-op diet is often harder than recovery itself. <strong>2 weeks (sometimes 4) of restrictive eating before surgery.</strong> But it's medically critical—NOT optional. It shrinks your liver by 15-30%, making surgery safer. Surgery may be cancelled if you don't follow it. This guide provides everything: WHY, WHAT, HOW, meal plans, and survival tips.</p>
</div>

<div class="info-box blue">
  <h4>🏥 Based on OSSANZ & Dietitians Australia Guidelines</h4>
  <p><strong>Key stats you need to know:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Liver shrinks <strong>15-30%</strong> in just 2 weeks on pre-op diet</li>
