    <p style="color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>What it is:</strong> Complete meal replacement shakes, 3-4 shakes per day (800-1,000 calories total), nutritionally complete, no solid food.</p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
      <div style="background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h4 style="color: #065f46; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1rem;">✅ Pros:</h4>
        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #064e3b; font-size: 0.95rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Simple (no meal planning)</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Guaranteed nutrition</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Most studied approach</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">Fastest liver shrinkage</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h4 style="color: #991b1b; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1rem;">❌ Cons:</h4>
        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 0.95rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Expensive ($100-$150 for 2 weeks)</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Boring (same flavor daily)</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Taste aversion common</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">Social situations difficult</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #1e3a8a; margin: 0;"><strong>Who it's for:</strong> Patients who need simplicity, surgeon requires it, or want zero meal planning.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 6px solid #10b981; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
