    <p style="color: #064e3b; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>What it is:</strong> 800-1,000 calories daily, &lt;50g carbs, high protein (60-80g), small portions of solid food.</p>

    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; margin: 1rem 0;">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem;">
        <div>
          <h4 style="color: #065f46; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1rem;">✅ Allowed:</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #064e3b; font-size: 0.95rem;">
