            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Non-starchy vegetables</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Protein shakes</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">Small amounts low-fat dairy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 style="color: #991b1b; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1rem;">❌ Avoided:</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 0.95rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Carbs (bread, pasta, rice)</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Sugars, fruit (most)</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">High-fat foods</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">Alcohol</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #064e3b; margin: 0;"><strong>Who it's for:</strong> Patients who cook, surgeon allows solid food, want variety.</p>
  </div>

