      <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Plan for Social Situations:</strong> Tell friends/family you're preparing for surgery. Avoid restaurants if possible. If must go out: Order protein + vegetables, eat half. Don't attend food-focused events.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Join Support Groups:</strong> Online bariatric surgery groups. Find others doing pre-op diet. Share struggles, tips, encouragement. Accountability helps.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Visual Reminders:</strong> Write surgery date on calendar. Count down days. Remember WHY you're doing this. Picture post-surgery success.</li>
